      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一个人总要走陌生的路，看陌生的风景，听陌生的歌，然后在某个不经意的瞬间，你会发现，原本是费尽心机想要忘记的事情真的就那么忘记了。<br><a id="more"></a></p><p>One is always  on  a strange road  ,watching  strange  scenery  and  listening  to strange music .<br>Then one day ,you  will  find that  the things you try hard  to forget   are  already  gone.</p>]]></content>
      
